          <figure class="hero-img">
            <img src="img/hero.png">
          </figure>
          <div class="col-1-2 push-1-2">
            <h1>Develop <strong><em>fast</em></strong>, <strong>rich</strong> &amp; <strong>beautiful</strong> applications in minutes.</h1>
            <div class="box-download">
              <a class="button-primary" href="http://github.com/bigcommerce/mozart">Mozart (GitHub)</a>
